content: Hey Bob, how's it going? Anything interesting happening lately?
Hey Alice, things are going well. Just keeping busy with work and such. Nothing too exciting, but I'm happy to be here and talking to you.

Hey Bob, I'm glad to hear that you're doing well. So, I wanted to ask you about something. Do you remember that time when we were in high school and we used to have this secret password to get into our secret hideout? Do you still remember what that password was?
